  <description><![CDATA[<p>Gressoney holidays offer classical Italian walking and cycling with spectacular Monte Rosa and Matterhorn shttps://www.inghams.co.uke prettiest villages in the glorious Monte Rosa Alps. Gressoney is situated https://www.inghams.co.https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/italy" title="italy"&gt;Italian-<a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/switzerland" title="swiss">Swiss</a> border.</p>
<p>Book your summer holidays in Gressoney and you'll experience a region that is studded with dramatic 4,000m peaks, crowned by the Monte Rosa itself and the equally mighty Matterhorn.</p>
<p>Linked to the neighbouring valleys of <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/italy/champoluc" title="champoluc">Champoluc</a> and Alagna. Holidays to Gressoney offer walkers and activity seekers of all levels, with 200kms of marked trails to choose from. There is also a wealth of museums and historic churches to visit locally, as well as the Castle Savoia and its famed botanical gardens.</p>]]></description>
